In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Roger N. POWELL. No. D-3032. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 29, 2018.

Roger N. Powell, of Reisterstown, Maryland, is suspended from the practice of *448law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
